snippet.title: DNF DUEL｜Nintendo Switch Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
📢 DNF Duel is now available on Nintendo Switch! 
Battle on-the-go with Nintendo Switch - Anytime, Anywhere!
Play as your favorite character and battle with your friends online. 

✨Shop Now: https://dd.nexon.com/en/products/switch-package

✨Twitter: https://twitter.com/DNFDuel_EN
